  "description": {
    "zh": "你好兄弟！你来的正是时候，我正收拾着准备去打猎呢。帮我个忙吧，这可不是在替我干活，就把它当作友谊的象征吧。在我回来的路上，我需要你去安排几个休息点。找个安全的地方，留下一盒俄式MRE和几瓶水，行吗？",
    "en": "Hello there! You came right in time, I'm just packing up to go hunting. Do me a favor, not for service, but as a sign of friendship. Arrange a couple of rest spots for my way back: the trip is long, so I'll have to stop for a breather somewhere. The places should be safe, leave a Russian MRE and a bottle of water for each, agreed? At the same time, remember how to survive if you get caught with your pants down. I've got some stashes hidden here and there, for example, but you don't need to know about them yet."
  },
